Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.17,0:00:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.73,0:01:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OVA第一话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.64,0:01:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,WATER·WAR！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.10,0:01:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.54,0:01:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一战的赛场在南方的小岛上！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.36,0:01:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.22,0:01:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah~~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然开场说了一句“所以呢”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.26,0:01:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是到底是为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.83,0:02:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定俗成的吐槽真像小桃桃的风格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.71,0:02:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要叫我小桃桃啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 难得有海滩 大家不如下水游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.50,0:02:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还真是个好点子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.87,0:02:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞成赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.50,0:02:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美穗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.78,0:02:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我..没有泳衣..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.25,0:02:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.61,0:02:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有学校指定的那件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.92,0:02:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大家一起去买吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.62,0:02:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百货公司里面有很棒的店哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.65,0:02:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！大家一起去买泳衣吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.35,0:02:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.75,0:02:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡是和泳衣沾边的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.11,0:02:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种各样一应俱全就是这家店的卖点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.10,0:02:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从古至今？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.79,0:02:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无奇不有？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 所有种类
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再现了庞贝壁画的最古老的两件式泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.40,0:02:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,19世纪的泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.63,0:02:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜闻乐见的条纹泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古今东西的电影明星穿着的时尚名牌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连封面女郎穿着的泳装也可以找到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.63,0:02:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是梦幻的吸睛泳衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人..穿这个会受欢迎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要乱讲啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.77,0:03:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个看起来不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哔嗡~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是淑女们最爱的花纹泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这件是走少女风格的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魅力无法挡啊 果然要这样才对嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥特风的泳衣 一直很想穿穿看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.82,0:03:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这款是带有佩斯利花纹的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上这件我就是风韵熟女了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.83,0:03:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是比起这些..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.25,0:03:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得今年的主流会是战车风哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.62,0:03:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战车？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.35,0:03:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 就是战车！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.54,0:03:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指的是豹纹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.54,0:03:25.63,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(705,660)}Panther
