Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.63,0:03:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是战车！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.63,0:03:26.34,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,660)}Panzer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.73,0:03:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说以前常把"潘塔"念成"潘萨"战车呢
