Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.73,0:03:29.32,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,660)}Panther
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.73,0:03:29.32,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(820,660)}Panther
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.78,0:03:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 就是战车！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意义不明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.85,0:03:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的是 比如大胆搭配转轮图案的这款泳衣..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量采用网格状布料
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.68,0:03:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜撸..喜撸什么来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装甲裙板对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:42.33,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(590,660)}schurzen
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:42.33,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}注：二战末期，配备大幅精简的四号J型坦克开始采用铁网状装甲裙板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外装式的辅助装甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这种款式的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透着一股南国风味 很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个标志是..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.26,0:03:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 这是非洲军团式样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 就是这样的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这个！还有这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么连我也要..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 这是英国第七装甲师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.86,0:04:03.50,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}M3斯图亚特轻型坦克：二战美国研制的一款轻型坦克 主炮 37mm gun M5/M6 \N500米穿深 54/78mm（APC/APCR）最大时速 56km/h 装甲 26-38mm
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.16,0:03:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通称“沙漠之鼠”式样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错 我觉得今年一定会流行这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧~~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是..是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得永远不会流行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校指定的就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真的有不少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑哪个好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.51,0:04:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼前突然冒出这么多品种的话..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了吗~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.59,0:04:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.31,0:04:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇~好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦吼~好可爱好可爱好可爱好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背后全开..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这款又如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈~这边也超可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后方注意..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看啊 这个这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DUI的干式潜水衣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:36.81,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}DUI："DIVING UNLIMITED INTERNATIONAL"某专业潜水器材品牌，\N一套CLX450潜水衣折合软妹币约18000圆，谢谢惠顾~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海豹突击队也在用它哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.26,0:04:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么高端还是免了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.59,0:04:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这个如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.65,0:04:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话又太成人向了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.77,0:04:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人困扰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明穿学校指定的就好了说..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得更可爱的比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要轻飘飘的或者有花纹的才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻飘飘的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 轻飘飘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.00,0:04:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻飘飘..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.97,0:04:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻飘飘的哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:04:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻飘飘到底是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样子滴！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正可谓围裙轻飘飘官爷吃不消！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.58,0:05:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻飘飘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撇去迷彩以外的话..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我穿这个就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻子这个不对啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.43,0:05:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有在听我说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.88,0:05:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话更绅士一点的更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优花里！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.23,0:05:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件泳衣是旧款式的死库水 简称旧水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.19,0:05:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这泳衣的用法还真深不可测呢..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻子 穿这个穿这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷泉同学 这件也很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷泉同学快穿上去 很漂亮哦..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.57,0:05:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看这件 好可爱..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.37,0:05:24.25,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯~嗯~嗯~嗯~嗯~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.25,0:05:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特种部队的一整套装备如何啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.82,0:05:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说选个正常点的啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件怎么说呢..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色兜裆布！红色兜裆布！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱历史爱兜裆布！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然该穿六文钱的红色兜裆布
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.31,0:05:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是非洲军团式样的椰子树图案比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到罗马军团就是甲胄！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有红围巾！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.93,0:05:49.63,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}盔甲泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上海援队的红白纹才对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:51.31,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}海援队：江戶时代后期幕末脱藩浪士们以坂本龙马为中心结成的贸易组织。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真田绳也难以割舍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:52.87,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}真田绳：一种用木棉丝织成的平实厚重的线，传说由真田昌幸·信繁父子制作出来。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.14,0:05:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是穿由德国开发出来的能溶于水的泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.73,0:05:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好的还是这件印有家纹的肚兜泳衣是也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的玩法好像很厉害的样子..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的情况变得有点莫名其妙..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:13.46,Zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(353,577)\frz18}踢水板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边的场面感觉好恐怖..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说你说 这件和这件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪一件更可爱啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.43,0:06:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先看我的 这件和这件哪件更适合我？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海豹突击队式样和英国SBS\N以及法国海军Commando还有俄罗斯特种部队..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个比较好？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.71,0:06:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金泳衣银泳衣~你要的是哪一件？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐~是哪件啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都太松了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.42,0:06:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们知不知道羞耻啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小桃桃 说服力为负
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.06,0:06:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错 这种时候不好好玩怎行呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.91,0:06:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家有在尽兴玩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.29,0:06:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.45,0:06:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一声！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.98,0:06:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一声！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.25,0:06:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:06:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.33,0:07:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来这世上还有这么多种类的泳衣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔来点战车之外的东西也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.18,0:07:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明穿学校指定的就好了说..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果自己还不是买了件蛮下限的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘记买了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.84,0:07:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是替您买了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？但是尺寸呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的三围目测技能点满了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸围82
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.20,0:07:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腰围56
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臀围84
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.35,0:07:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.62,0:07:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体测量仪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.12,0:07:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海耶！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.30,0:07:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备周全了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.93,0:07:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那开游了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一名~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不让给你~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.17,0:00:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.17,0:00:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.17,0:00:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
